        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Family Conflict</h3>
        <p class="text-white/90 mb-6">Resolve family dynamics and improve relationships</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-white/80">
          <li>• Parent-child relationships</li>
          <li>• Sibling conflicts</li>
          <li>• Intergenerational issues</li>
          <li>• Family communication</li>
